public class LabeledSimpleDirectedGraphStructureTypeInfo<GB>
extends StructureTypeInfo<LabeledStructureVertex,DefaultEdge,GB,ListenableDirectedGraph<LabeledStructureVertex,DefaultEdge>>

This class defines the LabeledSimpleDirectedGraphStructure Structure-Type. This Structure-Type has:

  • A LabeledStructureVertex as a vertexType.
    getVertexFactory()
  • structure.DefaultEdge as edgeType
    getGraphFactory()
  • SimpleDirectedGraph as JGraphT-Type
    Note that since this is not a structure.ListenableGraph it has to be wrapped in a structure.ListenableDirectedGraph in order to make it usable for GrALoG. See getGraphFactory() for how this is accomplished here.
  • no support for a Structure-Bean.
    getStructureBeanFactory()

Author:
Sebastian
